1539
01:36:57.227 --> 01:36:58.437
(LAUGHS MALICIOUSLY)

1540
01:37:04.276 --> 01:37:05.486
(SCREAMING)

1541
01:37:16.914 --> 01:37:19.375
The last Christmas.

1542
01:37:29.468 --> 01:37:31.303
(SOFTLY) Not if you
still believe.

1543
01:37:33.722 --> 01:37:35.391
No!

1544
01:37:35.933 --> 01:37:37.685
(SCROOGE SCREAMING)

1545
01:37:45.734 --> 01:37:46.735
(LAUGHS)

1546
01:37:52.825 --> 01:37:54.118
(CONTINUES LAUGHING)

1547
01:37:54.201 --> 01:37:55.244
(GUNSHOTS)

1548
01:38:04.002 --> 01:38:07.381
I have no idea what
the fuck is going on here.

1549
01:38:10.175 --> 01:38:11.552
But this ends now.

1550
01:38:16.932 --> 01:38:18.684
Damn right it does.

1551
01:38:21.186 --> 01:38:22.521
(ENGINES REVVING)

1552
01:38:28.193 --> 01:38:29.862
LINDA: Trudy.
be careful.

1553
01:38:33.699 --> 01:38:35.117
TRUDY: Santa!

1554
01:38:36.076 --> 01:38:37.995
Oh. no. Santa.

1555
01:38:39.538 --> 01:38:40.789
Oh. no.

1556
01:38:48.005 --> 01:38:49.965
You saved
my daughter.

1557
01:38:50.924 --> 01:38:52.217
SANTA: No.

1558
01:38:53.343 --> 01:38:54.762
She saved me.

1559
01:38:55.345 --> 01:38:57.639
Help him.
Please help him.

1560
01:38:57.765 --> 01:39:00.058
Honey. I don't think
there's anything we can do.

1561
01:39:00.184 --> 01:39:01.351
SANTA: It's okay.

1562
01:39:02.102 --> 01:39:03.562
It's too late for that.

1563
01:39:03.687 --> 01:39:04.938
Too late.

1564
01:39:06.690 --> 01:39:07.858
I'm cold.

1565
01:39:08.400 --> 01:39:09.526
(WINCES)

1566
01:39:09.610 --> 01:39:11.612
I haven't felt cold
in years.

1567
01:39:12.279 --> 01:39:13.781
We need
to keep him warm.

1568
01:39:15.157 --> 01:39:16.909
All of the fires
are going out.

1569
01:39:17.034 --> 01:39:18.660
We need to find
something to burn.

1570
01:39:20.621 --> 01:39:22.039
I got an idea.

1571
01:39:28.587 --> 01:39:29.963
No.

1572
01:39:30.088 --> 01:39:32.216
No. no. no. no.
No. Jason. no.

1573
01:39:32.341 --> 01:39:33.342
TRUDY: Please. Santa.

1574
01:39:33.884 --> 01:39:35.886
I don't want
you to die.

1575
01:39:39.556 --> 01:39:41.058
ALVA: Jason. let's
slow this down.

1576
01:39:41.183 --> 01:39:42.684
What are you doing?

1577
01:39:43.644 --> 01:39:46.063
I've lived longer than
any man should ever live.

1578
01:39:46.188 --> 01:39:48.690
He's pretty much dead.
What the hell is happening?

1579
01:39:48.816 --> 01:39:50.776
You don't need to burn money.
JASON: Okay. More. Yeah.

1580
01:39:50.943 --> 01:39:54.154
You can't die. Santa.
You have to get up.

1581
01:39:54.279 --> 01:39:56.740
I think I used up
all my Christmas magic.

1582
01:39:58.075 --> 01:39:59.243
Sorry.

1583
01:40:01.537 --> 01:40:05.082
I'm sorry I can't give
you what you asked for.

1584
01:40:06.708 --> 01:40:08.502
JASON: Take that. Take that.

1585
01:40:09.044 --> 01:40:10.337
TRUDY: But you did.

1586
01:40:13.632 --> 01:40:15.509
Santa. please don't die.

1587
01:40:15.634 --> 01:40:18.178
Wake up. Wake up.

1588
01:40:18.303 --> 01:40:20.013
JASON: We need to
get him close to the fire.

1589
01:40:20.848 --> 01:40:22.015
Jason.

1590
01:40:23.642 --> 01:40:25.310
Just wake up.

1591
01:40:26.478 --> 01:40:27.771
Please.

1592
01:40:28.063 --> 01:40:29.481
No.

1593
01:40:34.778 --> 01:40:36.947
Oh. I am
So. SO sorry.

1594
01:40:42.327 --> 01:40:43.620
This man...

1595
01:40:46.123 --> 01:40:49.459
This brave. brave man.
whoever he was...

1596
01:40:49.585 --> 01:40:50.836
He's Santa.

1597
01:40:51.378 --> 01:40:53.130
The real Santa.
He is.

1598
01:40:53.755 --> 01:40:55.591
And I still believe
in him.

1599
01:40:57.175 --> 01:40:59.553
I'll always believe
in you. Santa.

1600
01:41:04.516 --> 01:41:06.184
I believe
in him. too.

1601
01:41:09.521 --> 01:41:10.856
He saved Trudy.

1602
01:41:12.274 --> 01:41:13.817
He saved our family.

1603
01:41:16.612 --> 01:41:18.155
What's realer
than that?

1604
01:41:23.118 --> 01:41:24.286
Yeah. and maybe...

1605
01:41:27.456 --> 01:41:28.707
I believe
in him. too.

1606
01:41:30.000 --> 01:41:31.293
Uh. So do |I.

1607
01:41:33.003 --> 01:41:35.255
Oh. Shit.

1608
01:41:35.464 --> 01:41:37.090
(SNIFFLES)
I guess...

1609
01:41:38.091 --> 01:41:39.551
I guess I do. too.

1610
01:41:40.135 --> 01:41:41.553
ALVA: Fuck me.

1611
01:41:41.929 --> 01:41:43.305
I believe. too.

1612
01:41:53.023 --> 01:41:54.107
(COUGHS)

1613
01:41:54.191 --> 01:41:55.567
(GASPS)
Oh. my God.

1614
01:41:55.692 --> 01:41:56.777
Santa!

1615
01:41:58.445 --> 01:42:00.322
(GROANING)

1616
01:42:02.240 --> 01:42:03.325
JASON: You...

1617
01:42:05.285 --> 01:42:06.411
You were dead.

1618
01:42:08.038 --> 01:42:09.206
Christmas magic.

1619
01:42:10.749 --> 01:42:12.834
I still don't really
understand...

1620
01:42:13.669 --> 01:42:15.003
...how it works.

1621
01:42:16.505 --> 01:42:18.090
(SANTA CHUCKLES)

1622
01:42:21.426 --> 01:42:22.803
Thank you.

1623
01:42:23.095 --> 01:42:24.846
I don't know how we
can ever repay you.

1624
01:42:25.514 --> 01:42:28.183
You brought me back from
the dead. so we'll call it even.

1625
01:42:29.893 --> 01:42:31.019
Even?

1626
01:42:31.144 --> 01:42:33.188
We just burned
half a million dollars.

1627
01:42:34.523 --> 01:42:35.941
Look. Santa!
Hmm?

1628
01:42:36.066 --> 01:42:37.234
Look who came.

1629
01:42:39.319 --> 01:42:41.947
(REINDEER SNUFFLING)

1630
01:42:44.741 --> 01:42:47.452
Now you show up. huh?

1631
01:42:48.203 --> 01:42:49.663
You leave me
here to die.

1632
01:42:49.788 --> 01:42:51.915
come back after all
the work's done. huh?

1633
01:42:52.040 --> 01:42:54.626
You know what? I should
make you guys into a stew

1634
01:42:54.751 --> 01:42:56.294
and feed you
to the elves!

1635
01:42:57.004 --> 01:42:58.422
(REINDEER SNORTING)

1636
01:42:59.006 --> 01:43:03.385
Yes. Blitzen! Yes.
I'm talking to you!

1637
01:43:03.677 --> 01:43:05.470
You. too. Prancer.

1638
01:43:11.101 --> 01:43:12.519
You got my sack.

1639
01:43:13.270 --> 01:43:16.565
My spare... You went home
and you got my spare sack?

1640
01:43:19.359 --> 01:43:21.903
God. I can't stay mad
at you guys. I...

1641
01:43:23.280 --> 01:43:27.159
Aw. I can't. I can't.

1642
01:43:31.747 --> 01:43:32.873
Oh.

1643
01:43:34.207 --> 01:43:35.208
Oh.

1644
01:43:45.093 --> 01:43:46.344
Hello. beautiful.

1645
01:43:46.887 --> 01:43:47.929
Skullcrusher!

1646
01:44:01.318 --> 01:44:02.527
Guess this
is goodbye.

1647
01:44:02.944 --> 01:44:04.196
I gotta go.

1648
01:44:05.405 --> 01:44:06.656
Do you have to?

1649
01:44:10.869 --> 01:44:12.954
It's Christmas Eve.
and there's a lot of

1650
01:44:13.080 --> 01:44:14.623
boys and girls
on the nice list

1651
01:44:14.748 --> 01:44:16.374
that want their
presents. you Know?

1652
01:44:19.169 --> 01:44:20.504
Thank you.

1653
01:44:21.713 --> 01:44:23.048
For what?

1654
01:44:23.465 --> 01:44:24.716
For believing in me.

1655
01:44:25.759 --> 01:44:28.011
For reminding me that
Christmas still matters.

1656
01:44:29.971 --> 01:44:31.389
And that I still...

1657
01:44:32.557 --> 01:44:33.767
...matter.

1658
01:44:36.561 --> 01:44:38.146
You gave me
my "Ho. ho. ho" back.

1659
01:44:48.657 --> 01:44:50.408
All right.
Get out of here.

1660
01:44:54.538 --> 01:44:57.249
Merry Christmas!

1661
01:44:59.876 --> 01:45:01.128
Hyah!

1662
01:45:01.211 --> 01:45:04.548
Now. Dasher! Now. Dancer!

1663
01:45:04.673 --> 01:45:06.716
Now. Prancer and Vixen!

1664
01:45:06.842 --> 01:45:10.053
On. Comet! On. Cupid!

1665
01:45:10.178 --> 01:45:13.098
On. Donner and Blitzen!

1666
01:45:13.223 --> 01:45:16.852
Come on.
you beautiful bastards!

1667
01:45:16.977 --> 01:45:20.063
We've got
some work to do!

1668
01:45:20.313 --> 01:45:22.691
Hyah!

1669
01:45:23.233 --> 01:45:25.777
Ho. ho. ho!

1670
01:45:25.902 --> 01:45:28.989
Merry Christmas!

1671
01:45:34.161 --> 01:45:35.871
(FESTIVE ROCK SONG PLAYING)

1672
01:46:57.494 --> 01:46:59.579
Hey. yo! What's Gucci.
squad fam?

1673
01:46:59.704 --> 01:47:02.666
It's the Bert Locker.
living the dream.

1674
01:47:02.791 --> 01:47:05.168
You know what? See
this guy? Dead as hell.

1675
01:47:05.252 --> 01:47:06.544
Santa's real.
all right?

1676
01:47:06.670 --> 01:47:08.338
Don't end up on
the naughty list.

1677
01:47:08.463 --> 01:47:09.673
Do better.

1678
01:47:09.798 --> 01:47:11.132
Bert Lightstone out.

1679
01:47:51.506 --> 01:47:52.799
(UPBEAT SONG PLAYING)

